      "content": "i've tried the mindfulness and the meds. they just numb me a little bit, but they don't change the fact that i'm trapped in this. it's like trying to put a bandaid on a broken bone. it's not about managing it anymore, it's just... it's the weight of it. sometimes i think the only real mercy would be if it all just stopped. just everything. total stillness.",
